<TEXT>
<TITLE></TITLE>
<DATELINE></DATELINE>
<BODY>Was the leader of the Soviet Union from the mid-1920s until his death in 1953.</BODY>
</TEXT>
</REUTERS>

<REUTERS>
<DATE></DATE>
<TOPICS></TOPICS>
<PLACES></PLACES>
