<EXCHANGES></EXCHANGES>
<COMPANIES></COMPANIES>
<UNKNOWN></UNKNOWN>
<TEXT>
<TITLE></TITLE>
<DATELINE></DATELINE>
<BODY>Germany later violated the agreement and launched a massive invasion of the Soviet Union in June 1941. Despite heavy human and territorial losses, Soviet forces managed to halt the Nazi incursion after the decisive Battles of Moscow and Stalingrad.</BODY>
</TEXT>
</REUTERS>

<REUTERS>
<DATE></DATE>
<TOPICS></TOPICS>
<PLACES></PLACES>
