<EXCHANGES></EXCHANGES>
<COMPANIES></COMPANIES>
<UNKNOWN></UNKNOWN>
<TEXT>
<TITLE></TITLE>
<DATELINE></DATELINE>
<BODY>After defeating the Axis powers on the Eastern Front, the Red Army captured Berlin in May 1945, effectively ending the war in Europe for the Allies.[5][6] The Soviet Union subsequently emerged as one of two recognized world superpowers, the other being the United States.</BODY>
</TEXT>
</REUTERS>

<REUTERS>
