<UNKNOWN></UNKNOWN>
<TEXT>
<TITLE></TITLE>
<DATELINE></DATELINE>
<BODY>The Northern Expedition in China became a point of contention over foreign policy by Stalin and Trotsky. Stalin wanted the Communist Party of China to ally itself with the Nationalist Kuomintang, rather than attempt to implement a communist revolution.</BODY>
</TEXT>
</REUTERS>

