<TEXT>
<TITLE></TITLE>
<DATELINE></DATELINE>
<BODY>During the early morning of 22 June 1941, Adolf Hitler broke the pact by implementing Operation Barbarossa, the German invasion of Soviet held territories and the Soviet Union that began the war on the Eastern Front.</BODY>
</TEXT>
</REUTERS>

