<TEXT>
<TITLE></TITLE>
<DATELINE></DATELINE>
<BODY>Already in autumn 1940 Stalin received a warning of the Dutch Communist Party, via the network of the Red Orchestra, that Hitler was preparing for a winter war by letting construct thousands of snow landing gears for the Junkers Ju 52 transport planes.</BODY>
</TEXT>
</REUTERS>

